# ðŸ”¥ flamethrower

The ultimate debugging experience.

## Usage
1. Clone repo
```
git clone git@github.com:scottsus/flamethrower.git
```

2. Install requirements
```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

3. Export openai key
```
export OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-xxxxxxx
```

4. Run flamethrower
```
python main.py

```

5. Use as cli (optional)
```
# TODO: clean build.sh
```

